Distribution:   Azure Linux
Name:           capstone
Version:        5.0.1
Release:        1%{?dist}
Summary:        A lightweight multi-platform, multi-architecture disassembly framework

License:        BSD-3-Clause AND BSD-4-Clause AND APSL-2.0 AND NCSA AND MIT
